---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section class="capabilities" aria-labelledby="capabilities-title">
  <div class="shell">
    <SectionHeading
      id="capabilities-title"
      label="Built around the words"
      title="More than a microphone shortcut."
      description="Vaani gives the transcript context after it arrives: how it should read, which words matter, what phrases should expand, and what happened over time."
    />

    <div class="chapters">
      <article class="chapter chapter--capture">
        <div class="chapter__copy">
          <span class="chapter__number">01 / Capture</span>
          <h3>Dictate without changing workspaces.</h3>
          <p>Use push-to-talk or hands-free recording while messages, documents, terminals, and forms remain in front of you.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>System-wide voice input</li>
            <li>Background chunking for longer recordings</li>
            <li>Terminal-friendly paste behavior</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="chapter__visual capture-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="app-list">
            <span>Mail</span><span>Notes</span><span>Terminal</span><span>Browser</span>
          </div>
          <div class="capture-visual__field">
            <small>Reply</small>
            <p>I’ll review the changes this afternoon.<i></i></p>
          </div>
          <div class="mini-flow"><b></b><span>Vaani inserted 7 words</span><strong>✓</strong></div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="chapter chapter--refine">
        <div class="chapter__visual refine-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="refine-card refine-card--spoken">
            <span>Spoken</span>
            <p>“hey just wanted to check if the launch is still happening friday”</p>
          </div>
          <div class="refine-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="refine-card refine-card--written">
            <span>Work message · Casual</span>
            <p>Hey, just checking whether the launch is still happening on Friday.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="chapter__copy">
          <span class="chapter__number">02 / Refine</span>
          <h3>Keep the thought. Shape the delivery.</h3>
          <p>Optional cleanup can remove filler and adjust wording. App-aware styles help messages, email, and longer writing sound appropriate without changing the intent.</p>
          <p class="chapter__disclosure">Requires the optional language-model deployment you configure.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="chapter chapter--remember">
        <div class="chapter__copy">
          <span class="chapter__number">03 / Remember</span>
          <h3>Teach Vaani what you say often.</h3>
          <p>Keep names, jargon, acronyms, preferred spellings, and repeatable blocks of text close to the dictation workflow.</p>
          <div class="remember-tags" aria-label="Dictionary examples">
            <span>VaaniFlow → VaaniFlow</span>
            <span>kube control → kubectl</span>
            <span>weekly update → saved snippet</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="chapter__visual remember-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <header><span>Personal dictionary</span><b>+ Add term</b></header>
          <div><strong>VaaniFlow</strong><small>Exact spelling · Starred</small></div>
          <div><strong>kubectl</strong><small>Heard as “kube control”</small></div>
          <div><strong>Acme North</strong><small>Project name</small></div>
          <footer>Stored on this device</footer>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="chapter chapter--review">
        <div class="chapter__visual insights-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="insight-stat"><span>Words dictated</span><strong>12,480</strong><small>On this device</small></div>
          <div class="insight-bars">
            <i style="--h: 38%"></i><i style="--h: 66%"></i><i style="--h: 48%"></i><i style="--h: 78%"></i><i style="--h: 54%"></i><i style="--h: 92%"></i><i style="--h: 70%"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="insight-meta"><span>Mon</span><span>Today</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="chapter__copy">
          <span class="chapter__number">04 / Review</span>
          <h3>See what your voice produced.</h3>
          <p>Search local history and review word counts, dictation speed, streaks, and application usage without sending an analytics profile to VaaniFlow.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .capabilities {
    padding-block: var(--space-10);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
  }

  .chapters {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-9);
    margin-top: var(--space-9);
  }

  .chapter {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.78fr) minmax(0, 1.22fr);
    gap: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 8rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .chapter:nth-child(even) {
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.22fr) minmax(0, 0.78fr);
  }

  .chapter__copy {
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .chapter__number {
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .chapter h3 {
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-4);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-variation-settings: 'wdth' 88;
    font-weight: 610;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .chapter__copy > p,
  .chapter li {
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-size: 0.91rem;
    line-height: 1.72;
  }

  .chapter ul {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .chapter li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.15rem;
  }

  .chapter li::before {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.78em;
    left: 0;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-ink);
    content: '';
  }

  .chapter__disclosure {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem !important;
  }

  .chapter__visual {
    min-width: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-white);
    box-shadow: 0 22px 65px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.36);
  }

  .capture-visual {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 480px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #141719, #1b1f21 58%);
  }

  .app-list {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
  }

  .app-list span {
    padding: 0.45rem 0.7rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    border-radius: 5px;
    background: var(--color-white);
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.58rem;
  }

  .capture-visual__field {
    width: min(78%, 560px);
    margin: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 7rem) auto 0;
    padding: var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .capture-visual__field small,
  .refine-card span,
  .remember-visual small,
  .insight-stat span,
  .insight-stat small {
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .capture-visual__field p {
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 540;
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .capture-visual__field i {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 2px;
    height: 1em;
    margin-left: 0.12em;
    transform: translateY(0.1em);
    background: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .mini-flow {
    position: absolute;
    right: var(--space-5);
    bottom: var(--space-5);
    left: var(--space-5);
    display: grid;
    min-height: 64px;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: 0.7rem 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    border-radius: 15px;
    background: #080a0b;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .mini-flow b {
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #f2f4f5 0 2px, transparent 2px 5px);
  }

  .mini-flow span {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .mini-flow strong {
    display: grid;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-void);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }

  .refine-visual {
    display: grid;
    min-height: 500px;
    align-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    background: #121517;
  }

  .refine-card {
    padding: var(--space-4);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .refine-card p {
    margin: var(--space-3) 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.3vw, 2.1rem);
    font-weight: 520;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .refine-card--spoken {
    margin-right: 12%;
  }

  .refine-card--written {
    margin-left: 12%;
    border-color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .refine-arrow {
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .remember-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
  }

  .remember-tags span {
    padding: 0.55rem 0.7rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);
    color: var(--color-graphite);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
  }

  .remember-visual {
    min-height: 440px;
    padding: var(--space-4);
  }

  .remember-visual header,
  .remember-visual > div,
  .remember-visual footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .remember-visual header {
    min-height: 64px;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-ink);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  .remember-visual header b {
    padding: 0.5rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
    background: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-void);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
  }

  .remember-visual > div {
    min-height: 88px;
    padding-block: var(--space-3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-soft-rule);
  }

  .remember-visual strong {
    font-size: 0.86rem;
  }

  .remember-visual footer {
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding-top: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
  }

  .insights-visual {
    display: grid;
    min-height: 480px;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    background: #060708;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .insight-stat {
    display: grid;
    align-content: start;
  }

  .insight-stat span,
  .insight-stat small {
    color: #9aa3aa;
  }

  .insight-stat strong {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
    font-variation-settings: 'wdth' 82;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.07em;
    line-height: 0.9;
  }

  .insight-stat small {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
  }

  .insight-bars {
    display: flex;
    height: 180px;
    align-items: end;
    gap: clamp(6px, 1vw, 12px);
    margin-top: auto;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28);
  }

  .insight-bars i {
    width: 100%;
    height: var(--h);
    background: var(--color-ink);
    opacity: 0.84;
  }

  .insight-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 0.7rem;
    color: #9aa3aa;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .chapter,
    .chapter:nth-child(even) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }

    .chapter:nth-child(even) .chapter__visual {
      order: 2;
    }

    .chapter__copy {
      max-width: 680px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 719px) {
    .chapters {
      margin-top: var(--space-8);
    }

    .capture-visual,
    .refine-visual,
    .remember-visual,
    .insights-visual {
      min-height: 410px;
    }

    .app-list span:nth-child(n + 4) {
      display: none;
    }

    .capture-visual__field {
      width: calc(100% - 32px);
    }

    .refine-card--spoken {
      margin-right: 5%;
    }

    .refine-card--written {
      margin-left: 5%;
    }
  }
</style>
